The shredding New Jersey trio Screaming Females return on February 24 with their sixth album, Rose Mountain. Rose Mountain was produced by Matt Bayles (Mastodon, the Sword). After self-producing their earliest records, they worked with Steve Albini on their 2012 album Ugly and 2014's Live at the Hideout
